data.title: Southwest Portland Little League
data.text: Hitchen Field is located just off the primary parking area of Southwest Community Center. (corner of SW 45th and Vermont). Little Gabriel ("Little Gabe") is located in the southeast corner of Gabriel Park. The field must be accessed off of SW Multnomah Blvd. Turn north on SW 40th and then west (left) on Canby street. Parking is limited and must be shared with the off-leash dog area and community garden. Softball fields are across the road from the soccer fields. Field 3 is closest to the road.
